      "required": false,
      "setOfCodes": "&:AND;!:OR;",
      "helpText": "This field allows the ADPAC to indicate whether the conditions specified  by User Class and User Role should be logically \"AND'ed,\" or logically \"OR'ed,\"  as they will be unless otherwise specified.  i.e., if you want to specify  that an unsigned discharge summary may be signed by a user, where:  User Class = Provider AND User Role = Author,  then you'll want to set this field to AND. ",
